Do you believe in sin?</i>

00:21.271 --> 00:23.649
WOMAN [WHISPERING]:
There's nothing to believe.

00:27.903 --> 00:35.903
"The battle against the Devil, which is the principal task of Saint Michael the Archangel, is still
being fought today, because the Devil is still alive and active in the world." Pope John Paul ll

00:41.667 --> 00:46.286
What follows is inspired by true events.

03:25.414 --> 03:27.280
-You finished?
-Yep.

03:27.749 --> 03:29.956
Then wash up and come eat.

03:30.127 --> 03:31.868
I've washed up.

03:34.715 --> 03:36.706
Well, then eat.

03:38.635 --> 03:42.799
And when you're done,
I'll need a hand with the casket.

03:51.440 --> 03:53.226
How'd she do it'?

03:53.775 --> 03:55.391
What?

03:55.819 --> 03:57.480
Kill herself.

03:57.654 --> 03:59.986
Michael, I've told you this many times.

04:00.157 --> 04:02.990
We serve the dead,
but we don't talk about them.

04:03.869 --> 04:06.452
It brings bad things.

04:06.621 --> 04:09.329
We keep dead people in the house, Dad.

04:09.499 --> 04:11.706
How much worse could it get?

05:03.053 --> 05:05.420
-Are you kidding me?
-No, Eddie. I'm not kidding.

05:05.597 --> 05:06.678
Wait, Why'?

05:07.474 --> 05:08.930
So I can get out of here.

05:09.100 --> 05:13.310
Why not tell him you wanna go to college?
I mean, you got the grades. You can do it.

05:13.480 --> 05:17.064
-You think he'd pay for that?
-Shit, man. Seminary school?

05:17.234 --> 05:19.851
Wait, wait, wait. Wait.
Seminary school, really?

05:20.695 --> 05:24.404
Wait, is this your way of telling me
you're gay? I'm just joking. Okay? joking.

05:24.574 --> 05:28.568
Man, you don't get it. In my family, you're
either a mortician or a priest. That's it.

05:28.745 --> 05:30.827
Well, then change your name.

05:30.997 --> 05:34.581
It's too late. I took the entrance exam.

05:34.751 --> 05:36.287
-You what?
MICHAEL: I passed.

05:38.046 --> 05:39.878
I'm leaving Monday.

05:40.549 --> 05:42.506
EDDIE:
That'sâ€” That's crazy.

05:42.676 --> 05:44.041
MICHAEL:
Dude, I've looked into it.

05:44.219 --> 05:46.756
It's a four-year degree
before you even take your first vows.

05:46.930 --> 05:49.137
If it doesn't work out, I can always leave.

05:49.933 --> 05:53.051
Wow. Such faith.

05:53.436 --> 05:55.723
MICHAEL: You know what, Eddie?
You're such a dick.

05:55.897 --> 05:57.854
EDDIE:
Cool. Awesome. Whatever, dude.

05:58.024 --> 06:01.483
I will never confess to you.
You know that, right'?

06:01.653 --> 06:02.814
NINA:
These are on the house.

06:02.988 --> 06:05.070
EDDIE: Wow.
-Gonna get heat for giving away beers?

06:05.240 --> 06:06.605
Not if they don't know.

06:06.783 --> 06:08.569
How about for banging the customers?

06:09.035 --> 06:10.571
Screw you, Eddie.

06:11.538 --> 06:13.404
Drink up. I'm off in 10.

06:13.582 --> 06:15.414
Lickety-split.

06:18.211 --> 06:20.794
"Lickety-split"? Pbbb.

06:20.964 --> 06:25.049
You better make the most of that
before they chop your wiener off.

06:27.053 --> 06:28.885
Goodbye, wiener.

07:06.760 --> 07:08.751
ISTVAN:
Don't worry.

07:09.220 --> 07:11.837
The pain is gone.

07:13.058 --> 07:15.766
God has taken it...

07:16.311 --> 07:18.018
...away.

07:22.442 --> 07:25.230
Michael. Come.

07:28.156 --> 07:30.363
Don't be afraid.

07:53.974 --> 07:55.009
Four years later

07:55.183 --> 07:57.800
MAN:
<i>This is always a special Mass for</i> me...

07:57.978 --> 08:00.595
<i>...as I look upon our new deacons...</i>

08:00.772 --> 08:05.232
<i>...as they prepare to go into the world
with Christ's message.</i>

08:05.694 --> 08:09.107
So in the next few months,
you will face your last assessments...

08:09.280 --> 08:13.239
...and then be asked to take
your final vows to become priests.

08:13.410 --> 08:18.530
So I leave you with these words to
consider, from the Gospel of Saint John:

08:19.499 --> 08:22.412
You did not choose me...

08:22.919 --> 08:25.251
...it was I who chose you...

08:25.922 --> 08:31.213
...and I send you forth
to bear fruit that will last.

08:32.095 --> 08:34.587
[CROWD APPLAUDING]

08:54.159 --> 08:55.741
MATTHEW:
Michael.

08:56.911 --> 08:58.242
Exam results.

08:58.413 --> 08:59.619
You aced psychology.

09:00.040 --> 09:03.453
-Art history too. Congratulations.
-Thank you.

09:04.210 --> 09:06.542
So, what happened with theology?

09:07.088 --> 09:08.920
It's like you blew it on purpose.

09:09.090 --> 09:11.798
I've been distracted.
End of the year, that's all.

09:12.218 --> 09:14.960
Drop by my office this week.
We'll discuss it.

09:15.346 --> 09:16.928
Okay-

09:17.640 --> 09:20.348
[GUNFIRE PLAYING
ON VIDEO GAME]

09:22.479 --> 09:24.720
MAN:
Yeah, jump. Take him out.

09:34.824 --> 09:36.030
Dude, honestly?

10:23.540 --> 10:24.701
MATTHEW:
Michael!

10:24.874 --> 10:25.909
Michael, wait!

10:26.084 --> 10:27.700
[GRUNTS]

10:30.130 --> 10:32.246
[WOMAN SCREAMS]

10:46.896 --> 10:48.933
MICHAEL:
Call an ambulance!

11:05.915 --> 11:07.747
Bless me, Father.

11:11.462 --> 11:12.748
Father.

11:13.464 --> 11:15.205
Bless me.

11:17.760 --> 11:19.046
Please, Father.

11:19.971 --> 11:22.178
I don't wanna die like this.

11:26.603 --> 11:29.686
Uh, through the power vested in me:

11:29.856 --> 11:34.771
Let the fire of the Holy Spirit descend,
that this being may be awakened...

11:34.986 --> 11:38.650
...in the world beyond
the life of this earth...

11:39.115 --> 11:42.528
...and infused with the power
of the Holy Spirit.

11:42.952 --> 11:46.070
Lord Jesus Christ, I ask
that you receive this child-

11:46.956 --> 11:48.663
What's your name?

11:50.126 --> 11:52.458
Sandra.

11:56.716 --> 12:01.005
I ask you to receive this child,
Sandra, into your loving arms...

12:01.179 --> 12:04.388
...that she might pass in safety
from this crisis...

12:04.557 --> 12:06.719
...as you have taught us
with infinite passion.

12:06.893 --> 12:11.182
By this sign, you are anointed with the grace
of the atonement of our Lord Jesus Christ...

12:11.356 --> 12:14.348
...and absolved of all past error
and freed to take your place...

12:14.525 --> 12:16.983
...in the world he has prepared for us.

12:18.154 --> 12:20.270
[SPEAKING IN LATIN]

12:24.452 --> 12:26.159
Amen.

12:39.634 --> 12:44.003
[BELL TOLLING]

12:57.694 --> 12:59.856
[KNOCKING]

13:00.029 --> 13:02.020
[DOOR OPENS]

13:05.368 --> 13:06.483
Michael.

13:07.704 --> 13:10.787
I still don't even understand
how it happened.

13:11.582 --> 13:13.869
You shouldn't think about it.

13:14.210 --> 13:16.542
It was an accident. Really.

13:17.046 --> 13:18.423
It's hard not to think about.

13:18.923 --> 13:21.415
I feel somewhat responsible.

13:22.302 --> 13:25.385
You know the average age
of a nun these days?

13:25.763 --> 13:27.140
Sixty-nine.

13:27.682 --> 13:31.346
Three thousand parishes across the U.S.
don't even have a priest anymore.

13:31.519 --> 13:33.977
You give this speech
to everyone who tries to leave?

13:34.147 --> 13:37.390
No, just those I believe in.

13:38.276 --> 13:40.392
I quit smoking and
now I'm addicted to these.

13:51.497 --> 13:55.411
You know, what I saw the other night,
it was really something.

13:55.585 --> 13:58.247
I know experienced priests
who wouldn't have handled that.

13:58.421 --> 14:02.085
I just repeated a few prayers
over a suffering girl.

14:02.300 --> 14:03.916
And the words meant nothing to you?

14:04.093 --> 14:07.506
Father, listen to me,
did you understand my letter?

14:08.348 --> 14:13.013
Yes, I decided not to
pass it on to my superiors.

14:13.186 --> 14:15.723
-Why not?
-I think you're making a mistake.

14:16.731 --> 14:21.316
I think this is the part where I say, "It's
not you, it's me" and "Let's just be friends."

14:21.736 --> 14:23.773
Here's the thing.

14:25.323 --> 14:26.859
Tastes like shit.

14:28.159 --> 14:32.699
If a seminarian doesn't complete his vows,
then under Article 15...

14:32.872 --> 14:37.241
...the Church has the right to convert
the scholarship to a student loan.

14:37.960 --> 14:41.999
That's over 100 grand of education
you'd owe us.

14:42.173 --> 14:43.504
Why would you do that?

14:43.674 --> 14:46.336
Oh, no, no, no.
I'm not saying I'm going to do it...

14:46.511 --> 14:48.422
---J'ust yet.

14:50.181 --> 14:54.266
You were a mortician
before you joined us, am I right?

14:54.685 --> 14:56.972
I imagine that means
you're not very squeamish.

14:57.146 --> 14:58.136
What is this about?

15:01.025 --> 15:06.862
Last year, the Vatican received over a half
a million reports of demonic possession.

15:07.031 --> 15:09.614
-That's something of a record.
-I'm still not following.

15:09.784 --> 15:11.320
An order has been passed down...

15:11.494 --> 15:17.331
...to place an exorcist in every diocese
across the U.S. by this time next year.

15:17.500 --> 15:22.336
As you might imagine, it's not
a highly sought-after position.

15:22.880 --> 15:24.837
There's a new program at the Vatican...

15:25.007 --> 15:28.750
"designed to reteach the clergy
the rite of exorcism.

15:29.512 --> 15:32.345
I've been asked to keep an eye out
for potential candidates.

15:32.515 --> 15:34.847
Wait a minute, you...

15:35.810 --> 15:39.144
You want me to be an exorcist'?

15:41.315 --> 15:42.567
Why?

15:42.733 --> 15:44.690
Why would you want me'?

15:44.861 --> 15:46.351
I don't know what I believe in.

15:46.529 --> 15:48.270
That's right.

15:48.448 --> 15:49.904
I remember in your letter...

15:50.074 --> 15:54.113
...you explained how you used
the priesthood to run away from things.

15:54.287 --> 15:57.530
The truth is, you could have run
in any direction, but you ran here.

15:58.291 --> 15:59.907
Why?

16:01.419 --> 16:02.659
Just take the course.

16:03.296 --> 16:07.085
And then if you still wanna leave when
you get back, we can talk about it then.

16:08.342 --> 16:12.757
Two months in Rome.
How bad could that be?

17:15.451 --> 17:18.193
Keep the change. Thank you.

18:00.454 --> 18:02.445
I'm guessing there's no cable.

18:30.192 --> 18:34.311
<i>MAN: By the time an exorcist is called
to assess a possible possession...</i>

18:34.488 --> 18:38.152
<i>...the parish priest would have ensured...</i>

18:38.326 --> 18:41.694
<i>...that all psychiatric explanations
had been exhausted.</i>

18:41.871 --> 18:45.239
<i>He would have questioned
the possessed himself...</i>

18:45.416 --> 18:48.875
<i>...and forwarded his assessment
on to his bishop.</i>

18:49.045 --> 18:51.537
<i>With the bishop's permission...</i>

18:51.714 --> 18:56.208
...an <i>exorcist is then summoned
to determine possession.</i>

18:56.385 --> 19:01.255
Often, early signs of a possession
are subtle.

19:01.724 --> 19:03.556
Social withdrawal...

19:03.726 --> 19:05.512
...apa'fi|'lY---

19:06.562 --> 19:10.556
...a persistent tremor in a limb.

19:11.400 --> 19:14.563
It can go unnoticed
until the victim is deep within...

19:14.737 --> 19:16.728
...the demonic spirit's grasp.

19:16.906 --> 19:20.570
This was taken at an exorcism in Turin.

19:21.702 --> 19:24.490
[WOMAN YELLING ON VIDEO]

19:25.998 --> 19:29.081
The woman survived without food or water
for eight weeks...

19:29.502 --> 19:31.960
...before the demon released her.

19:33.339 --> 19:38.755
This man's jaw spontaneously dislocated
while being read the Lord's Prayer.

19:38.928 --> 19:42.137
He made no physical contact
with any object...

19:42.306 --> 19:45.719
...nor was he met with
any physical force.

19:48.979 --> 19:52.768
Demons are the devil's foot soldiers...

19:52.942 --> 19:56.276
...often operating in groups
much like a squadron...

19:56.445 --> 19:57.856
...infesting their victims.

19:58.030 --> 20:00.692
It is the job of an exorcist...

20:00.866 --> 20:04.575
...to determine the number of
possessing demons and their names...

20:04.787 --> 20:08.496
msomething the demons protect
with great ferocity.

20:08.708 --> 20:10.540
And when the exorcist has a name...

20:10.710 --> 20:14.954
...he can then begin to
assert control over the entity...

20:15.131 --> 20:17.122
...and cast it out.

20:18.676 --> 20:20.292
Who have we here?

20:23.931 --> 20:25.888
-Michael Kovak.
-I'm sorry?

20:26.434 --> 20:28.391
[LOUDER]
Michael Kovak.

20:28.602 --> 20:30.263
Oh, yes.

20:30.438 --> 20:31.724
The American.

20:32.064 --> 20:36.604
-Yeah. Sorry I'm late.
-Yes, I prefer punctuality to apologies.

20:36.986 --> 20:38.943
Welcome. Sit down.

20:41.073 --> 20:44.486
[MAN YELLING ON RECORDING]

20:44.660 --> 20:47.823
MAN [IN RUSSIAN ON RECORDING]:
Die, priest, die!

20:51.167 --> 20:54.831
XAVIER: The most identifiable sign
of a possession...

20:55.004 --> 20:58.998
...is the negative reaction
to sacred objects.

20:59.550 --> 21:03.339
Crucifixes, holy water.

21:03.679 --> 21:05.795
The man that you have just heard...

21:05.973 --> 21:09.341
...was reacting to a crucifix
placed on his head.

21:09.518 --> 21:11.259
ANGELINA: Excuse me, Father.
XAVIER: Yes?

21:11.437 --> 21:14.350
ANGELINA: What if he was suffering from
the delusion that he's possessed?

21:15.065 --> 21:16.897
Wouldn't he react in the same way?

21:17.067 --> 21:22.187
XAVIER: Admittedly, it's very easy to
confuse psychotic illness with possession.

21:22.364 --> 21:26.107
It's up to the exorcist
to discern the difference.

21:26.327 --> 21:28.568
WOMAN:
So how do you do that?

21:28.746 --> 21:30.362
Well, there are many ways.

21:30.539 --> 21:34.703
For example, paranoid schizophrenics
are not aware that they're deluded.

21:34.877 --> 21:38.290
MICHAEL: Neither are the possessed while
they're being possessed, are they?

21:38.464 --> 21:41.877
But people who are possessed
have periods of lucidity. That's my point.

21:42.051 --> 21:43.416
So do schizophrenics.

21:43.594 --> 21:47.713
XAVIER: One can't suddenly manifest
abilities simply because one is deluded.

21:47.890 --> 21:51.554
The man on this tape is German.

21:51.727 --> 21:54.059
How does he spontaneously
speak Russian?

21:54.396 --> 21:58.060
How could a boy in a village in Africa
found 400 miles from his home...

21:58.234 --> 22:00.646
...claim that he was abducted by aliens?

22:00.820 --> 22:02.060
It's just as unlikely.

22:02.238 --> 22:05.151
But we're willing to call him crazy
and your German man not...

22:05.324 --> 22:08.191
...because he believes in aliens,
not God.

22:11.372 --> 22:15.411
XAVIER: We're not here
to scrutinize religion with science.

22:16.126 --> 22:22.247
The object of this course is to view
phenomena through the lens of faith.

22:22.424 --> 22:25.462
So which do you believe in,
aliens or God?

22:25.636 --> 22:27.843
The jury's out on both.

22:28.013 --> 22:30.050
Interesting perspective for a priest.

22:30.224 --> 22:31.965
I'm not a priest...

22:32.142 --> 22:33.758
...yet.

22:33.936 --> 22:36.098
So you're having a final fling
with atheism?

22:36.272 --> 22:39.856
Well, I guess it's more like an ex-girlfriend
who keeps coming around.

22:40.985 --> 22:42.350
WOMAN:
Angelina.

22:42.528 --> 22:45.395
[IN ITALIAN] We are going to the library.
Are you joining us'?

22:45.573 --> 22:47.439
[SPEAKING IN ITALIAN]

23:04.842 --> 23:06.958
XAVIER:
Thank you, gentlemen. See you at Mass.

23:07.136 --> 23:09.969
Michael. Walk with me a moment.

23:10.806 --> 23:13.298
I understand you were taught
by Father Matthew.

23:13.475 --> 23:14.977
MICHAEL:
That's right.

23:15.144 --> 23:17.977
XAVIER: He's a dear friend.
We studied together at Loyola.

23:18.147 --> 23:21.890
He's asked me to keep an eye on you.
He thinks you've got great potential.

23:22.067 --> 23:23.683
MICHAEL:
That's a lot of pressure.

23:23.861 --> 23:25.977
For both of us.

23:26.280 --> 23:28.487
What do you think of the course so far'?

23:28.657 --> 23:30.910
To be honest, I don't know
what to make of it.

23:31.076 --> 23:32.692
XAVIER:
I suspected as much.

23:32.870 --> 23:36.864
Tell me, Michael, do you believe in sin?

23:37.041 --> 23:40.409
Yeah, I just don't necessarily believe
the devil makes us do it.

23:40.878 --> 23:43.290
He that committeth sin is of the devil.

23:44.048 --> 23:46.335
Then that'd be all of us, wouldn't it?

23:46.508 --> 23:48.840
And if we're all of the devil,
how do we fight him?

23:50.763 --> 23:55.007
Tomorrow, I recommend you take
your doubts for a walk around Rome.

23:55.768 --> 23:58.851
You can pay a visit
to an old friend of mine.

23:59.229 --> 24:00.685
Father Lucas?

24:00.856 --> 24:03.018
He's Welsh. Jesuit.

24:03.192 --> 24:05.900
His methods are a little less orthodox.

24:06.070 --> 24:08.186
Studied under
Father Carmine De Filippis.

24:08.364 --> 24:11.573
MICHAEL: I don't know what that means.
-It means he knows his stuff.

24:11.909 --> 24:16.699
He'll be happy to provide you with
the kind of proof you seem to need.

24:17.373 --> 24:19.614
Excuse me, I have a Mass to say.

25:00.582 --> 25:03.244
[BELL TOLLING]

25:11.844 --> 25:15.883
[CATS MEOWING]

25:45.127 --> 25:46.242
[MEOWS]

25:46.420 --> 25:48.411
Jesus.

25:48.589 --> 25:50.296
[MAN SPEAKS IN ITALIAN]

25:51.508 --> 25:54.296
MICHAEL: Father Lucas?
-Yes?

25:54.720 --> 25:56.927
Hi. I'm Michael Kovak.

25:57.097 --> 26:00.761
-Oh. You're the American.
-Yeah.

26:01.143 --> 26:03.510
-You don't like cats?
-Not particularly.

26:03.687 --> 26:06.645
Welcome to Rome.
It's infested with cats.

26:06.815 --> 26:09.022
I've tried giving them names
but it's pointless.

26:09.193 --> 26:12.982
A cat won't come no matter what
you call it. They do as they please.

26:14.364 --> 26:16.321
Anyway, welcome.

26:20.162 --> 26:22.028
Make sure they don't come in.

26:23.665 --> 26:25.247
MICHAEL:
No. Hey, hey.

26:28.712 --> 26:30.669
Father Xavier tells me you're troubled.

26:30.839 --> 26:33.331
I don't think Father Xavier
explained the situation.

26:33.509 --> 26:35.671
He explained it well enough.

26:35.844 --> 26:37.585
I've arranged for you to meet someone.

26:37.763 --> 26:39.219
[KNOCKING]

26:39.389 --> 26:41.471
Speak of the devil.

26:46.021 --> 26:48.558
[LUCAS SPEAKING IN ITALIAN]

26:49.691 --> 26:51.523
[ADRIANA & ROSARIA SPEAKING
IN ITALIAN]

26:53.946 --> 26:57.064
[IN ITALIAN] God bless you, Father,
thank you for seeing us.

26:57.241 --> 26:59.858
LUCAS [IN ITALIAN]:
There's no need to thank me.

27:02.538 --> 27:05.030
Put it in the kitchen.

27:06.500 --> 27:08.207
[BOTH SPEAK IN ITALIAN]

27:08.377 --> 27:09.867
<i>LUCAS:
Sit down.</i>

27:13.882 --> 27:15.498
ROSARIA [IN ITALIAN]:
Have you fed them?

27:15.676 --> 27:18.043
LUCAS:
No, they don't need feeding.

27:19.179 --> 27:23.468
ROSARIA:
Lucia. Gabriella. Dante. Federico.

27:23.809 --> 27:25.891
[SPEAKING IN ITALIAN]

27:30.482 --> 27:32.064
ROSARIA:
Where's Hermione?

27:32.609 --> 27:33.986
LUCAS:
Come now.

27:34.153 --> 27:35.518
ROSARIA:
No. I want to see Hermione.

27:35.696 --> 27:37.733
After. Come.

27:45.080 --> 27:47.572
[SPEAKING IN ITALIAN]

27:52.254 --> 27:56.088
[IN ENGLISH] If you wanna watch, you have
to help me. I'll need to absolve you first.

27:56.258 --> 27:57.623
MICHAEL:
Help with what'?

27:57.801 --> 27:59.917
The exorcism. What do you think?

28:00.095 --> 28:02.803
Or you can stay down here
with her aunt.

28:03.390 --> 28:04.926
That could be fun.

28:05.100 --> 28:06.932
It's up to you.

28:07.186 --> 28:11.100
Whatever you do, don't address the girl
directly, no matter what she says.

28:11.273 --> 28:13.355
And if I ask you to hold her down...

28:13.525 --> 28:17.234
...it's best you grab her arms
from behind...

28:17.404 --> 28:19.736
...and try keeping her
in a seated position.

28:19.907 --> 28:22.365
The spirit is pretty devious.
Hasn't shown itself yet.

28:22.534 --> 28:24.696
-The spirit?
LUCAS: Yes. Spirit.

28:26.622 --> 28:28.954
Demon. The devil.

28:29.124 --> 28:32.287
If it hasn't shown itself,
how do you know she's possessed?

28:32.502 --> 28:34.960
All right, give me something,
anything that's yours.

28:36.965 --> 28:38.797
Put it in this.

28:39.134 --> 28:40.340
What is it, a dollar bill?

28:40.510 --> 28:42.672
Come on, do it. Quickly.
It's for your benefit.

28:43.847 --> 28:45.554
What else?

28:46.850 --> 28:48.716
Oh, yes. It's Michael, isn't it?

28:49.228 --> 28:52.471
I absolve you of any sins you may
have committed now or in the past...

28:52.648 --> 28:54.935
...in the name of the Father,
Son and Holy Spirit.

28:55.108 --> 28:57.850
-Amen.
-All right, come on.

28:59.655 --> 29:03.489
Oh, yes, one other thing. If it does manifest,
don't even look into the girl's eyes.

29:03.659 --> 29:06.947
Whatever you do, do not address it.
Do not speak to it. It's the devil.

29:07.120 --> 29:09.157
-Leave that to me. Do you understand?
-Cool.

29:09.331 --> 29:10.992
-Do you understand?
-Yeah, I get it.

29:11.166 --> 29:12.702
Well, just say so.

29:12.876 --> 29:15.368
Bow your head, keep praying
and good luck.

29:48.954 --> 29:50.695
LUCAS [IN ITALIAN]:
How are you?

29:51.039 --> 29:52.621
The same.

29:52.874 --> 29:54.865
LUCAS:
Have you eaten?

29:58.088 --> 30:00.420
What about your baby?

30:01.550 --> 30:03.882
You need to eat.

30:04.928 --> 30:06.635
[IN ENGLISH]
Okay.

30:08.682 --> 30:10.298
Um...

30:10.726 --> 30:13.559
[IN ITALIAN]
What's happened since Tuesday?

30:13.937 --> 30:17.805
ROSARIA: It won't stop now.
Even when I sleep it talks.

30:17.983 --> 30:19.974
[SPEAKS IN ITALIAN]

30:20.152 --> 30:21.517
[CHUCKLES]

30:22.112 --> 30:23.819
[IN ENGLISH]
Okay.

30:24.614 --> 30:26.867
Now she's gonna guess what's in the bag.

30:27.159 --> 30:29.275
Rosafla?

30:29.911 --> 30:31.572
[IN ITALIAN]
See the bag'?

30:31.747 --> 30:33.283
[ROSARIA SPEAKS IN ITALIAN]

30:33.457 --> 30:36.165
Tell me what's in it.

30:37.502 --> 30:38.913
How could I know that?

30:39.087 --> 30:41.203
Then I want you to guess.

30:44.134 --> 30:45.169
I don't know.

30:45.344 --> 30:47.335
Clear your mind and guess.

30:47.512 --> 30:49.970
It's not a test. Just guess.

30:50.140 --> 30:51.255
I don't want to.

30:51.433 --> 30:53.344
I'm ordering you to guess! Guess!

31:01.610 --> 31:05.854
[SPEAKS IN ITALIAN]

31:08.784 --> 31:10.570
<i>[||\|</i> ENGLISH]
Show her.

31:20.670 --> 31:22.456
There you are.

31:22.631 --> 31:24.747
Knowledge of the unknowable.

31:25.133 --> 31:26.965
It's the quickest test for possession.

31:27.135 --> 31:30.298
The devil is working in and through her
right now.

31:32.140 --> 31:33.551
Okay-

31:39.147 --> 31:40.683
Uh...

31:40.857 --> 31:43.349
[IN ITALIAN]
Did it tell you what was in the bag?

31:43.527 --> 31:44.642
[ROSARIA SPEAKING
IN ITALIAN]

31:44.820 --> 31:46.561
Is it talking now?

31:46.738 --> 31:48.445
What's it saying?

31:50.450 --> 31:52.828
Disgusting things.

31:52.994 --> 31:56.328
It's important you tell me.

32:00.710 --> 32:03.668
[WHISPERING INDISTINCTLY]

32:08.844 --> 32:11.506
LUCAS:
Has it told you its name yet?

32:13.807 --> 32:15.423
Do you know its name?

32:15.600 --> 32:16.761
Tell me its name.

32:16.935 --> 32:18.471
Tell me now.

32:33.368 --> 32:35.826
[LUCAS SPEAKING IN LATIN]

32:52.971 --> 32:55.554
[CELL PHONE RINGING]

32:57.225 --> 32:58.807
[SPEAKS IN ITALIAN]

32:59.519 --> 33:00.930
<i>[||\| ENGLISH]
In!</i>

33:04.733 --> 33:05.939
[MICHAEL SPEAKING IN LATIN]

33:06.109 --> 33:08.851
LUCAS [IN ITALIAN]: I can't talk now,
I'm in the middle of something.

33:13.783 --> 33:16.366
[ROSARIA GRUNTING]

33:16.536 --> 33:19.119
[LUCAS SPEAKING IN LATIN]

33:23.043 --> 33:26.252
ROSARIA [IN ITALIAN]:
Shut up, shut up.

33:26.588 --> 33:28.750
Shut up, priest.

33:29.508 --> 33:31.545
You must not touch me.

33:31.927 --> 33:33.258
You are disgusting.

33:33.512 --> 33:35.128
Keep your dirty hands off me.

33:35.305 --> 33:37.262
Shut up! You must not speak.

33:37.432 --> 33:38.763
Don't touch me!

33:39.059 --> 33:40.595
Go away, priest. Go away!

33:40.769 --> 33:43.101
You stink, you are disgusting.

34:09.214 --> 34:10.830
Rosaria.

34:12.050 --> 34:13.210
Rosaria.

34:14.302 --> 34:16.293
Open your mouth.

34:16.846 --> 34:18.462
[LUCAS SPEAKS IN ITALIAN]

34:19.139 --> 34:20.301
How do you feel?

34:20.475 --> 34:22.556
[SPEAKS IN ITALIAN]

34:27.899 --> 34:29.310
LUCAS [IN ENGLISH]:
Okay.

34:37.701 --> 34:39.658
Okay, that's it.

34:49.379 --> 34:51.335
MICHAEL:
Really? That's it'?

34:51.505 --> 34:54.248
Well, what'd you expect?
Spinning heads, pea soup?

34:58.430 --> 35:01.138
Spiritual liberation can take months,
sometimes years.

35:01.641 --> 35:03.848
So she's still possessed?

35:04.019 --> 35:05.180
Yeah.

35:05.353 --> 35:08.015
I know you don't believe me, but...

35:09.357 --> 35:10.893
Tell me...

35:12.193 --> 35:16.562
...does a thief or a burglar turn on the
lights when he's robbing your house? No.

35:16.740 --> 35:20.984
He prefers you to believe
that he's not there.

35:21.161 --> 35:24.153
Like the devil. He prefers you
to believe that he doesn't exist.

35:24.331 --> 35:30.043
It gets complicated when no proof of
the devil is somehow proof of the devil.

35:31.046 --> 35:32.628
Yeah.

35:42.223 --> 35:45.056
The interesting thing
about skeptics, atheists...

35:45.226 --> 35:50.221
...is that we're always looking
for proof, certainty.

35:50.398 --> 35:53.436
The question is, what on earth
would we do if we found it?

35:53.610 --> 35:55.226
-"We"?
-Oh, yes.

35:55.403 --> 35:58.987
There are times when I experience
a total loss of faith.

35:59.157 --> 36:01.819
Days, months when I don't know
what the hell I believe in.

36:01.993 --> 36:05.327
God or the devil,
Santa Claus or Tinker Bell.

36:05.622 --> 36:07.408
But...

36:08.625 --> 36:10.787
...you know, I'm just a man.

36:10.960 --> 36:13.338
I'm a weak man. I have...

36:14.631 --> 36:16.542
...no power.

36:17.300 --> 36:22.761
Yet there's something that keeps
digging and scraping away inside me.

36:23.264 --> 36:26.302
Feels like God's fingernail.

36:26.518 --> 36:29.681
And finally I can take
no more of the pain...

36:29.854 --> 36:34.269
...and I get shoved out
from the darkness...

36:34.442 --> 36:36.524
...back into the light.

36:37.862 --> 36:40.069
Something like that.

36:41.783 --> 36:44.115
[SPEAKS IN LATIN]

36:46.329 --> 36:48.286
Anyway, enough philosophizing
for one day.

36:48.456 --> 36:52.950
If you have any more questions,
you know where to find me.

36:55.296 --> 36:58.084
I got my eye on you. What you doing?

37:12.313 --> 37:15.146
[CHATTERING]

37:23.992 --> 37:26.324
[SPEAKING IN ITALIAN]

37:38.798 --> 37:40.960
[HORNS HONKING]

37:50.018 --> 37:52.430
You're in Rome and you go to McDonald's?

37:52.604 --> 37:53.639
Oh, hey.

37:54.189 --> 37:57.682
Come on. Let me buy you Italian coffee.

38:01.738 --> 38:04.856
ANGELINA: Where were you today?
Xavier kicked you out, didn't he?

38:05.033 --> 38:08.116
Yeah, I've plea-bargained down
from being burned at the stake.

38:08.328 --> 38:10.911
So you're just vacationing now
on the Church's dime'?

38:11.080 --> 38:13.242
Yeah, and yours.

38:14.125 --> 38:17.459
Seriously, why are you taking the course?

38:17.629 --> 38:20.121
Why are you?
Are they recruiting nuns for exorcists?

38:21.758 --> 38:22.964
"Nuns"?

38:24.594 --> 38:27.552
I'm sorry, I just naturally assumed...

38:27.722 --> 38:29.929
Yeah, naturally.

38:32.936 --> 38:35.553
Well, if you're not a nun,
why are you taking the course'?

38:36.898 --> 38:40.857
I'm a journalist. I'm covering
the course for an article.

38:41.027 --> 38:43.985
I see. And I thought
you were just buying me a coffee.

38:44.364 --> 38:48.278
There's a lot of interest in this.
A lot of debate.

38:51.079 --> 38:52.661
Look...

38:53.289 --> 38:55.405
...| know you saw Father Lucas today.

38:56.084 --> 38:59.748
I've been trying to get an interview
with him, but he's been reluctant.

38:59.921 --> 39:01.753
What is it you want?

39:02.382 --> 39:04.999
-I'd love to know what you saw.
-You're asking me to spy?

39:05.176 --> 39:07.918
No, I'm asking you to report
your own experiences.

39:09.055 --> 39:10.420
Listen...

39:11.266 --> 39:13.974
...I'm just interested in the truth.

39:14.936 --> 39:16.847
Seems like you are too.

39:19.274 --> 39:23.939
XAVIER: Just as there is a hierarchy
of angels, ranked in ascendant order...

39:24.112 --> 39:27.571
...so, too, is the realm of evil ranked.

39:27.740 --> 39:29.902
And just as each angel has a name...

39:30.076 --> 39:32.283
...so, too, does every demon.

39:32.453 --> 39:36.071
Beelzebub, Leviathan, Ba'a|.

39:36.249 --> 39:38.456
These are some of the names
we look for...

39:39.043 --> 39:41.580
...when performing an exorcism.

39:41.754 --> 39:43.415
[PEOPLE GASPING]

39:46.509 --> 39:48.887
Just bear with me one moment.

39:51.931 --> 39:56.516
Well, I think we should leave it there
and pick it up tomorrow. Thank you.

40:04.152 --> 40:06.143
Michael, how's my old friend Lucas?

40:06.321 --> 40:08.278
MICHAEL:
He's unorthodox.

40:08.448 --> 40:10.280
XAVIER:
No exorcism is orthodox.

40:10.450 --> 40:13.568
MICHAEL: He's treating a pregnant girl
that I believe needs psychiatric care.

40:13.745 --> 40:14.985
XAVIER:
You believe?

40:15.163 --> 40:17.450
Father Lucas has been doing this
longer than anyone I know.

40:17.624 --> 40:19.456
MICHAEL:
I'm telling you because I'm concerned.

40:19.626 --> 40:20.832
It's not uncommon...

40:21.002 --> 40:24.040
...to be overly concerned for the subject
in one's first exorcism.

40:24.213 --> 40:27.672
You have to see that
it is the demon that's in pain.

40:28.426 --> 40:30.838
Trust me. Father Lucas gets results.

40:31.012 --> 40:32.343
At what cost'?

41:12.428 --> 41:15.261
[KNOCKING]

41:21.229 --> 41:24.221
Oh. What can I do for you?

41:26.067 --> 41:27.102
LUCAS:
Rosaria.

41:27.276 --> 41:28.983
[IN ITALIAN]
You remember this man?

41:29.153 --> 41:31.485
He was sent by the Vatican.

41:32.490 --> 41:35.448
I want you to answer his questions.

41:36.452 --> 41:38.238
Hi.

41:38.413 --> 41:42.953
It was terrible to see you
go through your suffering.

41:43.209 --> 41:47.248
This is unimportant. Just nod.

41:47.422 --> 41:49.333
MICHAEL:
Do you remember any of it?

41:49.882 --> 41:53.671
He wants to know if you remember things
when the devil takes over your body.

41:55.513 --> 41:57.550
[SPEAKING IN ITALIAN]

42:01.936 --> 42:06.772
LUCAS [IN ENGLISH]:
She says it's like a dream or a nightmare.

42:24.208 --> 42:25.619
MICHAEL:
This is yours, yes?

42:26.627 --> 42:28.334
[MICHAEL SPEAKS IN ITALIAN]

42:29.881 --> 42:31.542
Do you know how it got in my pocket?

42:31.716 --> 42:33.957
[IN ITALIAN]
Did you put it in his pocket'?

42:34.552 --> 42:35.792
Tell the truth now.

42:36.471 --> 42:37.552
It wasn't me.

42:37.722 --> 42:39.429
LUCAS:
Then who was it?

42:40.391 --> 42:42.769
Rosaria, who was it?

42:44.103 --> 42:45.810
[SPEAKING IN ITALIAN]

42:48.649 --> 42:49.935
MICHAEL:
The devil?

42:50.193 --> 42:51.649
LUCAS [IN ENGLISH]:
Why would she lie'?

42:51.819 --> 42:54.732
-She's 16.
-Yes.

42:54.906 --> 42:56.647
And she's pregnant.

42:56.824 --> 42:58.360
Who's the father of her child?

42:58.534 --> 43:00.070
She won't say.

43:00.870 --> 43:03.077
Ask her who gave her
the bracelet, please.

43:03.247 --> 43:05.500
[LUCAS SPEAKS IN ITALIAN]

43:08.252 --> 43:10.914
LUCAS [IN ENGLISH]: Her father.
MICHAEL: And where is he now?

43:11.089 --> 43:13.330
LUCAS: He's gone away. He left the family.
MICHAEL: When?

43:13.508 --> 43:16.626
LUCAS: Oh, I don't know.
A few months ago, I believe.

43:19.931 --> 43:22.969
-What are you doing?
-I'm giving it back to her.

43:23.351 --> 43:26.434
[MICHAEL SPEAKING IN ITALIAN]

43:50.378 --> 43:52.790
[LUCAS SPEAKING IN LATIN]

43:52.964 --> 43:55.626
[GASPING AND GRUNTING]

44:09.981 --> 44:13.724
ROSARIA [IN DEMONIC VOICE IN ENGLISH]:
Remember the fat little bitch?

44:15.862 --> 44:18.024
Killed herself.

44:18.197 --> 44:19.904
She says to say hello.

44:20.575 --> 44:22.862
Hell-o.

44:24.245 --> 44:26.202
In the name of Jesus Christ,
name yourself.

44:26.372 --> 44:27.703
[ROSARIA WHISTLING]

44:27.874 --> 44:30.491
In the name of Jesus Christ,
name yourself.

44:30.960 --> 44:34.294
By the authority of Jesus Christ,
I command you to declare yourself!

44:34.755 --> 44:38.840
By the authority of Jesus Christ,
I command you to declare yourself now!

44:39.177 --> 44:41.544
ROSARIA [IN ITALIAN]:
We are the fruit of her womb.

44:41.721 --> 44:43.928
Speak the truth, in the name
of Jesus Christ.

44:44.098 --> 44:46.180
Speak the truth, in the name
of Jesus Christ.

44:46.350 --> 44:48.808
We're strong in the Lord
and the power of his might!

44:49.437 --> 44:54.773
ROSARIA:
In the name of Judas Cross.

44:54.942 --> 44:58.560
Demon, name yourself.
Your name, demon! Your name!

44:58.738 --> 45:00.320
Tremble before the Lord!

45:00.489 --> 45:03.277
We're strong in the Lord
and the power of his might!

45:03.451 --> 45:04.486
Now!

45:05.786 --> 45:08.494
By the authority of Jesus Christ,
I command you to-

45:08.664 --> 45:09.825
Hold her!

45:09.999 --> 45:11.080
Help me. Help me.

45:11.250 --> 45:12.536
MICHAEL:
Hail Mary, full of grace.

45:12.710 --> 45:15.122
The Lord is with thee.
Blessed art thou amongst women...

45:15.296 --> 45:17.788
[ROSARIA GRUNTING
AND SCREAMING]

45:18.925 --> 45:21.383
[LUCAS SPEAKING IN LATIN]

45:25.640 --> 45:27.881
[IN ENGLISH]
Shit on your Holy Spirit!

45:31.062 --> 45:32.803
LUCAS: He that dwelleth
in the secret place of the Most High...

45:32.980 --> 45:36.018
...shall abide under the shadow
of the Almighty. He is my refuge...

45:36.192 --> 45:37.933
...my fortress and my strength.

45:38.110 --> 45:40.488
He shall deliver thee
from the snare of the fowler...

45:40.655 --> 45:42.396
Rape me.

45:46.327 --> 45:48.409
â€”My fortress and my strength.

45:48.996 --> 45:50.498
Lickety-split.

45:53.668 --> 45:56.911
Thou shalt not be afraid for
the terror by night, nor for the arrow...

45:57.088 --> 46:00.080
...nor for the destruction that wasteth.
A thousand shall fall...

46:00.258 --> 46:01.874
...and 10,000 at thy right hand...

46:02.051 --> 46:04.509
ROSARIA [IN NORMAL VOICE IN ITALIAN]:
Father, please.

46:04.679 --> 46:07.171
Don't let it hurt my baby.

46:07.348 --> 46:10.511
They shall bear thee up in their hands,
lest thou dash thy foot against a stone.

46:10.685 --> 46:12.642
[LUCAS SPEAKING IN LATIN]

46:12.812 --> 46:15.019
ROSARIA [IN DEMONIC VOICE IN ENGLISH]:
Take it out!

46:16.232 --> 46:19.065
Shit it out and eat it!

46:26.867 --> 46:29.199
LUCAS: Our Father who art in heaven,
hallowed be thy name.

46:29.370 --> 46:32.283
Thy kingdom come, thy will be done
on earth as it is in heaven.

46:32.456 --> 46:36.871
Give us this day our daily bread and forgive
us our trespasses, as we forgive those...

46:37.044 --> 46:40.378
[IN NORMAL VOICE IN ITALIAN]
Help me.

46:41.841 --> 46:43.707
<i>[||\|</i> ENGLISH]
You...

46:44.260 --> 46:47.002
LUCAS: Hail Mary, full of grace.
The Lord is with thee.

46:47.221 --> 46:49.178
[IN DEMONIC VOICE IN ITALIAN]
Go to hell, priest!

46:49.348 --> 46:51.214
LUCAS:
Blessed is the fruit of thy womb, Jesus.

46:51.392 --> 46:53.929
Holy Mary, mother of God,
pray for us sinners...

46:54.103 --> 46:56.970
...now and at the hour of our death.
Amen.

46:57.732 --> 47:00.099
-Hail Mary, full of grace.
MICHAEL: She's choking. Father.

47:00.276 --> 47:02.984
LUCAS:
Pray with me! Out!

47:03.154 --> 47:07.398
And begone, you unclean spirits
of terror and darkness. Out!

47:07.742 --> 47:10.734
Damned Legion, Satan, Lucifer, out!

47:10.911 --> 47:13.118
Begone! We banish you,
we cast you out...

47:13.289 --> 47:17.499
...in the name of the Virgin Mary, mother
of Christ, the son of the living God...

47:17.668 --> 47:19.909
...in whom we live, and move,
and have our being.

47:20.087 --> 47:21.998
Who lives in us and reigns in us
supreme.

47:22.173 --> 47:24.756
We cast you out from
the nothingness and the darkness...

47:24.925 --> 47:28.839
...from whence you came.
Out, demon! Out, Lucifer! Out, Satan!

47:29.013 --> 47:31.380
Now! Begone! In the name
of the Holy Spirit.

47:32.808 --> 47:34.924
[ROSARIA COUGHS]

47:38.189 --> 47:41.227
LUCAS: Deliver this from the snare
of the fowler, from the pestilence...

47:41.400 --> 47:43.016
...from the darkness.

47:44.945 --> 47:47.403
[SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY]

47:59.085 --> 48:01.292
Well, she's asleep.

48:03.089 --> 48:05.046
She needs to rest.

48:05.216 --> 48:10.006
So I'll send her home in a few days
so she can recover.

48:13.641 --> 48:16.724
I thought you were required
to have a doctor present.

48:16.894 --> 48:18.726
I am a doctor.

48:21.190 --> 48:22.976
Has she seen a psychiatrist?

48:23.150 --> 48:26.017
-Yeah.
-What happened?

48:26.195 --> 48:28.152
Oh, she doesn't respond to treatment.

48:28.322 --> 48:31.656
-Is she on antidepressants?
-No.

48:32.034 --> 48:35.652
-No, she's pregnant.
-So she hasn't been medically treated?

48:35.830 --> 48:38.868
Yeah. I'm looking after her.

48:41.335 --> 48:43.702
Weren't you concerned for her health
up there?

48:43.879 --> 48:45.836
Yeah, of course I was.

48:46.006 --> 48:47.872
Well, how will her baby survive this?

48:48.050 --> 48:53.671
See, it's very difficult to predict how
any of this stuff is gonna work out.

48:56.642 --> 48:59.009
-Have you ever lost a patient?
-Yeah.

48:59.687 --> 49:03.726
Yeah, a boy I once treated.
He was about 15 years of age...

49:05.067 --> 49:07.559
...and he committed suicide...

49:08.362 --> 49:10.319
...and I was depressed
for a few months...

49:11.198 --> 49:14.611
...and I started to doubt everything
I believed in.

49:16.704 --> 49:19.321
And I thought the devil had defeated me.

49:22.460 --> 49:25.452
Don't you think she should
see a psychiatrist again?

49:28.340 --> 49:29.626
You're still not convinced-

49:29.800 --> 49:33.885
Oh, Christ! She was raped by her father.
She's internalizing her guilt.

49:35.473 --> 49:39.057
"Internalizing"? Okay.

49:39.727 --> 49:41.593
Still doesn't explain everything,
does it?

49:41.770 --> 49:44.478
It doesn't explain
how she started to speak English.

49:44.648 --> 49:48.312
Well, she's a teenager. She's listened
to a thousand songs on the radio.

49:50.070 --> 49:52.027
What about these nails?

49:52.239 --> 49:54.776
It could be that she swallowed them
to hurt the baby.

49:54.950 --> 49:56.281
She clearly doesn't want it.

49:58.496 --> 50:03.332
What about the voice inside her? That
wasn't a human voice, though, was it'?

50:04.960 --> 50:06.746
You be careful, Michael.

50:06.921 --> 50:08.252
Why?

50:08.422 --> 50:12.757
Choosing not to believe in the devil
won't protect you from him.

50:24.021 --> 50:26.058
ISTVAN [IN VOICE-OVER]:
Michael.

50:28.275 --> 50:29.265
Come.

50:43.541 --> 50:45.828
<i>Come closer.</i>

50:49.755 --> 50:53.623
You're not a coward. Don't be afraid.

50:55.010 --> 50:57.126
It's just your mother.

50:57.638 --> 50:59.003
Now...

50:59.640 --> 51:01.722
...blow.

51:02.476 --> 51:05.468
We want to do a good job, don't we?

51:06.397 --> 51:08.809
The best we can.

51:10.985 --> 51:13.477
Good. Now...

51:16.490 --> 51:18.322
...pray.

51:22.830 --> 51:26.323
Hail Mary, full of grace.
The Lord is with thee.

51:26.500 --> 51:29.709
Blessed art thou among women
and blessed is the fruit of thy womb...

51:29.878 --> 51:32.006
[IN HUNGARIAN]
My love.

51:33.299 --> 51:34.664
My flower.

51:34.842 --> 51:37.755
Mother of God, pray for us sinners...

51:38.762 --> 51:41.015
My beautiful.

51:41.181 --> 51:43.388
Amen.

52:08.083 --> 52:10.370
[WHISTLING]

52:10.544 --> 52:11.784
LUCAS:
Can't get enough, huh?

52:11.962 --> 52:15.876
Doing house calls today.
Take that, it's gonna rain.

52:17.259 --> 52:19.466
Shut the gate after you.

52:20.888 --> 52:23.220
[THUNDER CRASHING]

52:23.390 --> 52:25.882
[CHILDREN CHATTERING]

52:29.188 --> 52:30.519
LUCAS:
Vincenzo.

52:30.689 --> 52:34.227
[IN ITALIAN]
What happens in your dream?

52:34.610 --> 52:36.772
BOY [IN ITALIAN]:
I'm being hurt.

52:37.029 --> 52:38.611
LUCAS:
<i>By</i> what?

52:38.906 --> 52:40.863
<i>BOY:
A mule.</i>

52:41.033 --> 52:43.195
<i>With red</i> eyes.

52:45.663 --> 52:47.279
It kicks me.

52:47.456 --> 52:49.197
And bites me.

52:51.585 --> 52:53.667
LUCAS:
And do you try and run away?

52:53.837 --> 52:55.293
[VINCENZO SPEAKS IN ITALIAN]

52:56.173 --> 52:57.914
Why not?

52:58.258 --> 53:02.593
VINCENZO: Because he says he's my father
and I must obey him.

53:02.763 --> 53:04.549
Oh.

53:07.059 --> 53:08.891
What else does he tell you?

53:10.062 --> 53:11.769
He tells me...

53:17.152 --> 53:19.109
...to kill myself.

53:20.823 --> 53:22.734
FRANCESCA [IN ITALIAN]:
Show him.

53:27.788 --> 53:30.280
He woke up with these.

53:30.457 --> 53:32.289
[WINCES]

53:39.299 --> 53:41.290
[SPEAKS IN ITALIAN]

53:42.928 --> 53:43.963
[BRAYS]

53:44.138 --> 53:45.845
[LAUGHS]

53:47.641 --> 53:49.382
The mule from the dream?

53:50.144 --> 53:51.600
Vincenzo?

53:52.730 --> 53:55.893
The mule in the dream?

53:57.234 --> 53:58.975
Mama?

54:01.864 --> 54:03.775
Not Mama?

54:03.949 --> 54:05.656
[SPEAKING IN ITALIAN]

54:07.286 --> 54:09.152
You hit him?

54:09.705 --> 54:10.991
Are you lying'?

54:11.165 --> 54:12.826
Are you a liar'?

54:19.965 --> 54:21.751
Okay-

54:24.511 --> 54:25.842
Come here.

54:29.224 --> 54:31.340
Open your mouth.

54:31.518 --> 54:33.350
Ahh.

54:35.189 --> 54:38.022
Bring me his pillow.

54:44.740 --> 54:48.904
[SPEAKING IN LATIN]

54:52.372 --> 54:54.500
[SPEAKS IN ITALIAN]

55:05.761 --> 55:08.173
[IN ENGLISH] Banish all the forces of evil
from this pillow.

55:08.639 --> 55:11.472
Vanquish them. Destroy them!

55:13.227 --> 55:14.388
Now!

55:18.732 --> 55:19.722
Ah.

55:19.900 --> 55:21.561
[LAUGHS]

55:21.985 --> 55:25.774
[SPEAKING IN ITALIAN]

55:29.618 --> 55:31.154
[IN ITALIAN]
The devil!

55:42.673 --> 55:47.383
LUCAS [IN ENGLISH]:
We cast you out, every unclean spirit...

55:47.928 --> 55:50.386
...every Satanic power...

55:51.056 --> 55:54.549
...every onslaught of
the infernal adversary.

55:54.726 --> 55:57.593
Be gone and stay far
from this creature of God...

55:57.771 --> 56:01.230
...for it is he who commands you,
it is he...

56:01.400 --> 56:04.518
[INDISTINCT]

56:04.695 --> 56:05.935
[WHISPERING INDISTINCTLY]

56:06.113 --> 56:07.820
â€”He who would still the sea...

56:07.990 --> 56:09.901
...the wind and the storm.

56:10.075 --> 56:12.191
[WHISPERING INDISTINCTLY]

56:12.369 --> 56:15.782
â€”Flee, enemy of the faith,
you foe of the human race.

56:15.956 --> 56:21.292
That's enough now, do you hear me'?
No one is going to die.

56:21.461 --> 56:24.954
LUCAS:
â€”put the unholy tempter to flight.

56:25.132 --> 56:27.419
[SPEAKS IN ITALIAN]

56:27.593 --> 56:30.085
LUCAS:
â€”and of the Holy Spirit. Amen.

56:48.196 --> 56:49.903
[SIGHS]

56:51.783 --> 56:54.992
I'm supposed to take care
of this place...

56:56.288 --> 56:59.497
...but I feel so bad.
Never seem to have any time.

56:59.666 --> 57:02.283
You ever wonder if the people
you help are just mistaken?

57:02.461 --> 57:03.747
LUCAS:
Yeah. Sometimes, I suppose.

57:04.713 --> 57:06.920
MICHAEL:
But you still do what you do.

57:07.090 --> 57:09.752
LUCAS: Why not'? I haven't seen a prayer
hurt anyone yet.

57:09.927 --> 57:13.591
So you're happy to have them continue
believing something that may not be true?

57:13.764 --> 57:15.596
LUCAS:
Yes, why not'?

57:15.933 --> 57:18.641
And what is it you believe?

57:19.186 --> 57:22.429
I believe that people prefer to lie
to themselves than face the truth.

57:23.398 --> 57:27.266
The truth, yeah. Certainty.

57:27.444 --> 57:31.028
[PHONE RINGING]

58:17.911 --> 58:20.198
LUCAS [IN ITALIAN]:
I will leave immediately.

58:20.414 --> 58:22.576
I understand. Thank you.

58:25.877 --> 58:28.835
[IN ENGLISH]
Rosaria just tried to drown herself.

58:29.006 --> 58:32.419
[ROSARIA YELLING]

58:35.929 --> 58:39.422
[IN ITALIAN] We gave her pethidine
and trazodone but she won't calm down.

58:39.599 --> 58:42.011
Legally we can't give her anything else.

58:48.066 --> 58:50.933
ROSARIA:
Look what I've done to her, priest!

58:51.111 --> 58:53.603
And I'm not finished yet!

59:09.629 --> 59:11.882
[LUCAS SPEAKING IN LATIN]

59:25.479 --> 59:26.810
<i>LUCAS:
Leave it.</i>

59:27.522 --> 59:30.139
Let her see who is in command.

59:31.651 --> 59:34.313
Demon. Deceiver.

59:36.156 --> 59:37.863
Speak your name.

59:38.033 --> 59:39.990
[IN DEMONIC VOICE]
Neven

59:41.411 --> 59:43.072
LUCAS:
Why are you living in her?

59:43.246 --> 59:47.331
Because her suffering is sweet.

59:48.210 --> 59:49.746
LUCAS:
What do you plan to do with her?

59:49.920 --> 59:52.833
Eat the flies from her rotting flesh.

59:54.174 --> 59:55.756
LUCAS:
How did you enter her?

59:55.926 --> 59:57.837
With her father's seed.

59:58.011 --> 01:00:01.925
-So you remember being raped'?
LUCAS: Don't address it directly.

01:00:02.099 --> 01:00:07.765
[IN GREEK] When the devil has nothing
better to do, he rapes his children.

01:00:08.730 --> 01:00:09.765
I don't understand.

01:00:09.940 --> 01:00:11.601
[SPEAKS IN GREEK]

01:00:11.775 --> 01:00:14.642
[LAUGHING]

01:00:16.279 --> 01:00:18.441
You know how to swear
in every language?

01:00:18.615 --> 01:00:22.529
ROSARIA [IN LATIN]: Therefore let us
go down and confound their tongue...

01:00:22.702 --> 01:00:25.239
...that they may not understand
one another's speech.

01:00:26.206 --> 01:00:28.038
MICHAEL:
You know the Bible well.

01:00:28.208 --> 01:00:30.870
We know it very well.

01:00:35.799 --> 01:00:36.960
Very clever.

01:00:37.134 --> 01:00:39.000
[IN ENGLISH]
Don't patronize me, doubter!

01:00:39.427 --> 01:00:42.510
It is I who chose you.

01:00:43.056 --> 01:00:45.639
-Why do you call me "doubter"?
ROSARIA: Because it's true.

01:00:46.560 --> 01:00:49.018
A liar knows a liar.

01:00:51.648 --> 01:00:53.935
Are you a liar, Rosaria?

01:00:54.109 --> 01:00:56.271
What is it you want me to believe?

01:00:56.444 --> 01:00:58.151
There's nothing to believe.

01:00:59.322 --> 01:01:01.529
Then there is no devil
and you're not possessed?

01:01:01.825 --> 01:01:04.908
You fear me, mortal!

01:01:06.746 --> 01:01:09.283
How can I fear you if you don't exist?

01:01:31.771 --> 01:01:33.853
You think you outsmarted him?

01:01:35.066 --> 01:01:37.194
That's not the devil.

01:01:37.652 --> 01:01:40.189
It's just a very, very sick girl.

01:01:41.281 --> 01:01:44.114
She doesn't need a priest,
she needs a shrink.

01:01:46.411 --> 01:01:50.120
He still has you fooled, hasn't he?

01:01:54.502 --> 01:01:56.960
You forgot your bag of tricks.

01:02:01.801 --> 01:02:04.213
LUCAS:
He's a deceiver, Michael.

01:02:07.307 --> 01:02:09.719
He's a deceiver.

01:02:50.767 --> 01:02:54.305
[MONITOR BEEPING]

01:03:54.414 --> 01:03:56.872
[ALARM BEEPING]

01:04:06.051 --> 01:04:07.712
[ALARM BEEPING]

01:04:07.886 --> 01:04:09.843
[WOMAN SPEAKING IN ITALIAN
OVER SPEAKER]

01:04:15.185 --> 01:04:17.677
[IN ITALIAN]
Hold on. Hold on, Rosaria.

01:04:18.688 --> 01:04:21.476
[PEOPLE CHATTERING IN ITALIAN]

01:04:27.280 --> 01:04:30.773
MAN 1 [IN ITALIAN]:
This is a tragedy. How could this happen?

01:04:31.284 --> 01:04:35.949
Who worked here today?
I want to talk with everyone.

01:04:39.167 --> 01:04:41.374
MAN 2 [IN ITALIAN]:
Tell me about the mother.

01:04:42.337 --> 01:04:46.251
[IN ITALIAN] There was internal bleeding,
massive hemorrhaging.

01:04:49.260 --> 01:04:51.126
We did everything in our power...

01:04:51.304 --> 01:04:54.547
...but unfortunately
we couldn't save her or her baby.

01:05:05.443 --> 01:05:06.899
MICHAEL:
What now?

01:05:07.737 --> 01:05:09.478
Oh, nothing.

01:05:09.906 --> 01:05:11.817
It's finished.

01:05:12.492 --> 01:05:15.985
He took a life.
That's what he wants, ultimately.

01:05:17.330 --> 01:05:20.118
He'll probably find someone else.

01:05:23.628 --> 01:05:26.370
You should go home, get some rest.
You've had a hard night.

01:05:26.548 --> 01:05:28.380
Yeah.

01:05:31.678 --> 01:05:33.669
Are you okay?

01:05:36.433 --> 01:05:37.798
I failed her.

01:05:38.768 --> 01:05:41.260
You did what you thought was best.

01:05:42.230 --> 01:05:43.937
Yeah.

01:05:50.363 --> 01:05:52.195
<i>|</i> gotta go.

01:05:54.909 --> 01:05:56.320
Take care of yourself.

01:06:02.417 --> 01:06:04.499
You're a good man, Michael.

01:06:05.879 --> 01:06:08.120
You have a good soul.

01:06:08.965 --> 01:06:10.922
Defend it.

01:06:11.176 --> 01:06:12.917
Guard it.

01:06:13.720 --> 01:06:15.711
Cherish it.

01:06:18.308 --> 01:06:21.426
Oh, God. Oh, God.

01:06:21.603 --> 01:06:24.846
[SOBBING]

01:06:44.042 --> 01:06:46.079
-Hey.
-Thanks for coming.

01:06:46.252 --> 01:06:48.869
You picked a perfect day for it.

01:06:49.047 --> 01:06:50.412
I appreciate you doing this.

01:06:51.591 --> 01:06:54.879
-No names.
-No names. Promise.

01:06:55.053 --> 01:06:57.920
There's no way she touched the baby
because she was restrained.

01:06:58.097 --> 01:06:59.758
That's right.

01:07:00.141 --> 01:07:02.178
What do you make of that?

01:07:04.062 --> 01:07:05.427
It's confounding.

01:07:05.855 --> 01:07:08.313
That's the story.
It's yours to interpret as you will.

01:07:08.483 --> 01:07:10.975
You can call me
if you have any questions.

01:07:11.152 --> 01:07:12.267
Thank you.

01:07:16.616 --> 01:07:18.857
What changed your mind?

01:07:19.160 --> 01:07:20.616
To do this?

01:07:21.454 --> 01:07:24.071
I just needed to tell someone.

01:07:26.668 --> 01:07:28.284
ANGELINA [IN VOICE-OVER]:
So <i>let</i> me get this straight.

01:07:28.670 --> 01:07:32.334
You ran away from home
and chose a life of celibacy?

01:07:32.882 --> 01:07:36.125
-How bad could home be'?
-It sounds stupid when you say it like that.

01:07:36.302 --> 01:07:39.294
It sounds stupid
because it doesn't add up.

01:07:39.806 --> 01:07:42.639
Are you saying you never felt a calling?

01:07:43.643 --> 01:07:45.600
My mother...

01:07:45.812 --> 01:07:48.645
...she used to say
she felt the hand of God on me.

01:07:49.857 --> 01:07:50.983
Did you feel it?

01:07:52.402 --> 01:07:54.313
I wanted to.

01:07:57.323 --> 01:08:00.236
-So how did you end up in all this?
-It's a long story.

01:08:00.410 --> 01:08:02.071
We're not going anywhere,
SO come Ol"I.

01:08:04.372 --> 01:08:08.206
My parents committed my brother
to a mental institution when he was 19.

01:08:10.128 --> 01:08:11.914
He was so tormented.

01:08:12.088 --> 01:08:15.456
He said he heard voices
telling him to do things.

01:08:16.050 --> 01:08:18.917
He used to tell me
it was the devil speaking to him.

01:08:22.682 --> 01:08:25.890
Sometimes he would tell me
what the devil said.

01:08:29.397 --> 01:08:32.059
And sometimes the things he said
would come true.

01:08:34.027 --> 01:08:35.563
It frightened me.

01:08:36.279 --> 01:08:38.770
He frightened me.

01:08:40.867 --> 01:08:46.203
I know it sounds terrible, but it's just
easier when I don't think about him.

01:08:46.372 --> 01:08:50.036
[WHISTLES BLOWING]

01:09:23.533 --> 01:09:27.243
<i>YOUNG MICHAEL: Hail Mary, full of grace.
The Lord is with thee.</i>

01:09:27.412 --> 01:09:29.198
<i>Blessed art thou among women...</i>

01:09:29.374 --> 01:09:33.368
<i>...and blessed is the fruit
of thy womb, Jesus.</i>

01:09:33.544 --> 01:09:35.080
<i>Holy Mary...</i>

01:09:35.587 --> 01:09:37.920
<i>...mother of God...</i>

01:09:38.091 --> 01:09:41.755
<i>...pray for us sinners now
and at the hour of our death.</i>

01:09:41.928 --> 01:09:43.669
<i>Amen.</i>

01:10:22.552 --> 01:10:24.589
[KNOCKING]

01:10:26.681 --> 01:10:29.389
I'm sorry to wake you, Michael.

01:10:30.727 --> 01:10:32.764
I thought it best to tell you myself.

01:10:33.146 --> 01:10:35.137
It's your father.

01:10:36.816 --> 01:10:38.557
And he hasn't regained consciousness?

01:10:38.735 --> 01:10:41.147
<i>MAN [OVER PHONE]:
No. The stroke was massive.</i>

01:10:41.320 --> 01:10:44.403
<i>He could stabilize
or he could stay like this.</i>

01:10:44.574 --> 01:10:45.609
I see.

01:10:45.783 --> 01:10:49.196
<i>I'm sorry. There isn't much more
I can tell you at this point.</i>

01:10:55.334 --> 01:10:57.416
I'm sorry, Michael.

01:10:57.587 --> 01:11:00.204
I'll include him in my prayers.

01:11:03.676 --> 01:11:05.508
We can help arrange your travel.

01:11:07.889 --> 01:11:09.596
Thank you.

01:12:38.896 --> 01:12:41.354
You gotta be fucking kidding me.

01:12:45.236 --> 01:12:48.945
<i>WOMAN [ON TV]: Airlines are warning
passengers to expect more delays...</i>

01:12:49.115 --> 01:12:52.153
<i>...even when the dust from
the volcano in Iceland has settled.</i>

01:12:52.326 --> 01:12:56.786
<i>Tonight, the ash plume has shut the
airports of 22 countries on the continent...</i>

01:12:56.956 --> 01:13:01.746
<i>...with Italy and Switzerland among
the latest to close their airspace.</i>

01:13:01.919 --> 01:13:02.954
[SPEAKS IN ITALIAN]

01:13:03.129 --> 01:13:05.496
<i>Thousands of passengers are stranded,
with some being told...</i>

01:13:05.673 --> 01:13:07.880
<i>...it could be a week
before they get another flight.</i>

01:13:08.050 --> 01:13:09.632
-Once the ash clears...
-I need a room.

01:13:09.802 --> 01:13:12.339
<i>-...a</i> backlog of flights...
-[IN ENGLISH] No problem.

01:13:12.513 --> 01:13:16.632
<i>...will mean further disruption.
Valerie Rigg, Egetsa Coverage.</i>

01:13:16.809 --> 01:13:19.642
I'm calling to check
on my father's condition.

01:13:19.812 --> 01:13:21.473
Istvan Kova k.

01:13:21.647 --> 01:13:24.309
K-O-V-A-K.

01:13:24.483 --> 01:13:25.985
WOMAN [OVER PHONE]:
I'll connect you.

01:13:30.156 --> 01:13:33.148
[LINE RINGING]

01:13:35.995 --> 01:13:39.329
ISTVAN [OVER PHONE]: Michael.
-Yeah, yeah. It's Michael.

01:13:39.874 --> 01:13:41.615
<i>I'm scared.</i>

01:13:41.792 --> 01:13:44.329
It's okay. Dad, you're okay.

01:13:44.503 --> 01:13:48.497
<i>No. Something happened.</i>

01:13:49.342 --> 01:13:52.505
-It's okay, Dad.
-Where are you?

01:13:53.346 --> 01:13:54.711
<i>I</i> wish you were here.

01:13:54.889 --> 01:13:59.178
I'll be home soon.
Something happened with my flight.

01:14:00.311 --> 01:14:02.268
Where am I?

01:14:03.356 --> 01:14:05.347
You're in the hospital.

01:14:05.816 --> 01:14:07.898
[ISTVAN GRUNTS]

01:14:08.527 --> 01:14:10.689
What is it, Dad?

01:14:12.865 --> 01:14:14.526
Dad?

01:14:15.201 --> 01:14:17.317
<i>They're hurting me.</i>

01:14:17.495 --> 01:14:19.156
Who?

01:14:20.373 --> 01:14:21.863
Dad?

01:14:22.041 --> 01:14:24.783
MAN [OVER PHONE]: Mr. Kovak?
-Yeah.

01:14:24.961 --> 01:14:27.544
<i>-It's Dr. Vorachian.
-Yes.</i>

01:14:28.047 --> 01:14:32.507
<i>Mr. Kovak, I'm afraid
I've got some very bad news.</i>

01:14:32.677 --> 01:14:35.089
<i>Your father passed away this afternoon.</i>

01:14:37.848 --> 01:14:39.759
Uh, what?

01:14:40.559 --> 01:14:46.054
<i>Your father died this afternoon.
I'm very sorry, Mr. Kovak.</i>

01:14:46.607 --> 01:14:49.395
Well, that's impossible. I...

01:14:49.568 --> 01:14:52.401
I was just speaking with him, just now.

01:14:52.571 --> 01:14:57.065
<i>Mr. Kovak, your father was
declared dead about six hours ago.</i>

01:14:57.243 --> 01:14:59.280
<i>I was a witness.</i>

01:14:59.954 --> 01:15:02.742
<i>I'm very sorry to have to tell you...</i>

01:15:13.300 --> 01:15:16.008
[SOBBING]

01:15:31.527 --> 01:15:35.111
PRIEST: "Whoever lives by believing in me
will never die."

01:15:35.281 --> 01:15:38.273
Lord have mercy, Christ have mercy...

01:15:39.118 --> 01:15:41.109
...Lord have mercy.

01:15:41.287 --> 01:15:45.622
Eternal rest grant unto her, O Lord,
and let perpetual light shine upon her.

01:15:45.791 --> 01:15:47.452
May she rest in peace.

01:16:03.142 --> 01:16:05.099
ROSARIA [IN VOICE-OVER]:
Doubter!

01:16:24.080 --> 01:16:25.662
[WOMAN GASPS]

01:16:33.672 --> 01:16:37.210
[WOMAN CACKLING]

01:17:08.874 --> 01:17:10.785
ISTVAN [IN VOICE-OVER]:
Michael.

01:17:12.920 --> 01:17:15.207
ROSARIA: <i>A</i> liar <i>knows</i> a liar.

01:17:15.381 --> 01:17:17.839
[WOMAN CACKLING]

