01:39:36.387 --> 01:39:37.502
<i>No.</i>

01:39:37.889 --> 01:39:39.129
'Twas I.

01:39:40.725 --> 01:39:43.387
<i>You chose me long, long ago...</i>

01:39:44.061 --> 01:39:48.555
<i>...when you were just an itsy-bitsy
little boy pooping in his pants.</i>

01:39:48.733 --> 01:39:49.723
Remember, Michael.

01:39:49.901 --> 01:39:51.437
You remember, Michael?

01:39:51.611 --> 01:39:53.568
Remember when you bent that <i>cross?</i>

01:39:53.738 --> 01:39:56.070
<i>If only you remember.</i>

01:39:56.240 --> 01:39:57.651
Remember, Michael. Remember.

01:39:57.825 --> 01:39:59.907
Remember.

01:40:02.455 --> 01:40:03.741
Oh, dear.

01:40:03.915 --> 01:40:07.579
<i>[IN VOICE-OVER]
Our poor little savior all alone on his cross.</i>

01:40:09.045 --> 01:40:10.080
Yeah.

01:40:10.254 --> 01:40:13.337
God chose you, Michael.
That's why you're here.

01:40:14.175 --> 01:40:15.210
Just accept it.

01:40:15.384 --> 01:40:16.920
-Yeah.
ANGELINA: Accept God.

01:40:17.094 --> 01:40:19.256
LUCAS: Accept the devil.
-You can't win without him.

01:40:19.430 --> 01:40:20.465
No.

01:40:21.057 --> 01:40:22.092
All alone.

01:40:25.269 --> 01:40:26.521
[LUCAS SPEAKS
