01:40:26.687 --> 01:40:27.722
No!

01:40:32.109 --> 01:40:34.646
[ANGELINA GRUNTING]

01:40:38.616 --> 01:40:43.201
Shall I pour the sick and rotting truth
of the dying world...

01:40:43.371 --> 01:40:46.489
...into your precious, golden womb?

01:40:47.458 --> 01:40:49.870
You remember his strangling screams...

01:40:50.044 --> 01:40:53.253
...when you turned your back on him
and walked away?

01:40:53.422 --> 01:40:57.711
You wanted the truth, little lady.
Well, here I am.

01:41:01.305 --> 01:41:03.387
So how about you, kissy lips?

01:41:07.478 --> 01:41:10.311
Do you feel that probing around
inside you, Michael?

01:41:10.481 --> 01:41:12.142
Lucas, listen to me, please.

01:41:12.316 --> 01:41:14.694
Lucas is not here.

01:41:14.860 --> 01:41:16.237
He's never coming back.

01:41:18.531 --> 01:41:22.820
You feel that digging and scraping around
inside you like God's dirty fingernail?

01:41:23.869 --> 01:41:26.281
