01:41:39.010 --> 01:41:41.092
I believe in the devil.

01:42:04.869 --> 01:42:06.109
<i>I believe in you...</i>

01:42:08.080 --> 01:42:09.696
...so I believe in God.

01:42:12.376 --> 01:42:15.368
I accept him in this moment.
I accept God.

01:42:16.213 --> 01:42:19.547
I believe in God the Father,
the maker of heaven and earth...

01:42:19.717 --> 01:42:22.254
...of all that is seen and unseen.

01:42:22.428 --> 01:42:24.339
I believe.

01:42:24.513 --> 01:42:27.847
I exorcise you, most unclean spirit.

01:42:28.017 --> 01:42:30.554
Warp of vices, creator of agony.

01:42:30.728 --> 01:42:33.390
In the name of Jesus Christ,
leave this man.

01:42:33.564 --> 01:42:36.101
In the name of the Virgin Mary,
leave now.

01:42:36.317 --> 01:42:37.432
I command you.

01:42:37.902 --> 01:42:39.392
I, who believe.

01:42:39.570 --> 01:42:41.607
In the name of our Lord, Jesus Christ...

01:42:41.781 --> 01:42:44.569
...be uprooted and expelled
from this creature of God.

01:42:44.742 --> 01:42:47.700
He who commands you is he
who ordered you to be thrown down...

01:42:47.870 --> 01:42:50.407
...from the highest heaven
into the depths of hell.

01:42:50.581 --> 01:42:53.539
Hear therefore and fear,
Satan, enemy of faith.

01:42:53.709 --> 01:42:57.577
Fear him who was crucified as man
and who rose from death!

01:42:59.757 --> 01:43:01.464
I will never leave you, Michael.

01:43:05.012 --> 01:43:07.595
I will never leave you.

01:43:10.434 --> 01:43:12.687
[GROWLING AND THUDDING]

01:43:20.277 --> 01:43:21.779
Speak your name.

01:43:24.073 --> 01:43:27.907
In the name of Jesus Christ,
I command you, speak your name.

01:43:32.123 --> 01:43:35.991
In the name of the Holy Spirit,
I command you. Give me your name!

01:43:37.920 --> 01:43:40.787
It is God who commands you!
Your name!

01:43:41.132 --> 01:43:42.463
Your name!

