01:44:24.633 --> 01:44:26.920
Depart from this place. Leave!

01:44:27.428 --> 01:44:29.010
Surrender now.

01:44:29.180 --> 01:44:33.549
In the name of the Father, and
of the Son and of the Holy Spirit...

01:44:33.726 --> 01:44:35.842
