It's good as new, huh?

01:46:08.529 --> 01:46:10.019
Yeah.

01:46:10.948 --> 01:46:13.280
Well, she wasn't a bad little bike.

01:46:13.450 --> 01:46:15.316
You know, back in her golden days...

01:46:15.494 --> 01:46:17.656
