all those years ago.

01:46:18.455 --> 01:46:20.037
Anyway...

01:46:20.291 --> 01:46:22.407
So you're off. You're leaving.

01:46:22.585 --> 01:46:24.121
MICHAEL:
Yeah, that's right.

01:46:24.295 --> 01:46:28.129
