Safe journey. And one other thing.

01:47:06.337 --> 01:47:09.329
Faith becomes you. Stay with it.

01:47:09.506 --> 01:47:13.841
Keep fighting the good fight
with all thy might.

01:47:15.387 --> 01:47:17.128
Cool.

01:47:18.599 --> 01:47:20.135
